            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Genuine review after making my kid to spend 3 years in this school. My kid after studying in this school, his communication levels have become very poor that he is not even able to properly frame a sentence with right grammar. The school says they focus on discipline, communication and education but in really none of this happens. Teachers are not qualified to give that education foundation to kids.\n\nParent teachers meeting will be conducted twice or thrice a year in which you will not be given any opportunity to raise any concern. They talk only about the school’s achievement in that meeting. If a parent raise any concern in PTA meeting, that kid will be targeted in class which has led to impacting child psychologically. The quality of education is poor.\n\nWhile the school fees is less compared to other schools in this locality, but they will ask child to bring money almost every alternative day for some or other celebration which will amount to some thousands in the end of academic year.\n\nIf you are looking to make your child develop both in academics and in personality I will not suggest this school.",
